data.description: Come check this lovely townhouse!!!!! On the main floor there is a spacious family room and dining area leading to the updated bright kitchen featuring new granite countertops and floors installed in 2022, Laundry room located on main floor and a half bath. The upper level features 2 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The primary bedroom has a private bath with double vanities and plenty of under sink storage and a large walk-in closet . HOA fee covers water and sewer as well.
